Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:56.67,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}鼓動奮わせて居たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.52,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's unlimited  It's unlimited
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:04.02,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If I can believe myself again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:07.36,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光の中  目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:11.08,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてくれたキミとなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.33,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:13.50,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:16.98,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここで生まれ変わる景色
